org.datavec.api.transform.ops

Class AggregableMultiOp<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.api.transform.ops.AggregableMultiOp<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IAggregableReduceOp<T,java.util.List<Writable>>, Consumer<T>, Supplier<java.util.List<Writable>>

    public class AggregableMultiOp<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAggregableReduceOp<T,java.util.List<Writable>>
    This class transforms a list of IAggregableReduceOp on one single field, each returning a Writable and transforms it into an operation on that single column, that returns a Writable list. It is used to execute many reduction operations in parallel on the same column, datavec#238 Created by huitseeker on 5/8/17.
